## File References

- **ACTIVITY / READ / LAB files**: Human-readable link text with prefix
  - Format: `[ACTIVITY: Human-Readable Title](ACTIVITY_filename.md)`
  - Same for `[READ: Title](READ_filename.md)` and `[LAB: Title](LAB_filename.md)`
- **Code and script files**: Filename in backticks as link text
  - Format: ``[`filename.ext`](path/to/file.ext)``
  - Add brief description after: ``[`01_example.py`](01_example.py) â€” Python example``
- **Always use relative hyperlinks** when discussing files; never bare filenames
- In prose: "See [`plumber.R`](plumber.R)" not "See plumber.R"

